  /// * `latitude` - GPS latitude (exact)
  /// * `longitude` - GPS longitude (exact)
  /// * `update_interval_secs` - Publish-cadence hint used to compute the
  ///   jittered NIP-40 `expiration` tag on the outer kind:445 wrapper.
